metrics_conclusion: Mario Kart DS - Waluigi Pinball has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity and Chord Progression Novelty.
key_conclusion: Mario Kart DS - Waluigi Pinball has sections analyzed in the following keys: E Mixolydian,  and E Dorian.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments:
This track was composed by Shinobu Tanaka. Stop crediting music as "Nintendo". Real people made this music, not a faceless company. vgmdb.com has a huge database for videogame music credits resources!

Anyhow main chord in this piece is E7, not Em7. Also added the grace chords (Bbm7b5/E).
